Rust: stable (1.8x)
Hardware resonance: PhextCoord = 128 bits = 1 SSE register = ½ AVX-256

Layer Stack (bottom to top):

L0  Hardware        PhextCoord as 128-bit register value
L1  Addressing      11D coordinate lattice [0..2047]^11
L2  Temporal        TTSM: immutable block chain + fork/karma edit
L3  Memory          EpochPPT: versioned page translation, copy-on-write
L4  Execution       SIW: D/S/C pipes, ri() register safety, octawire
L5  Topology        Twisted pairs: 8 links/sentron, Wuxing generative
L6  Coherence       SentronSheaf: H¹=0 condition, global section assembly
L7  Admission       Bickford's Demon: DAG enforcement, knot detection
L8  Dynamics        Omega-process: Büchi acceptance, limit ordinal detection
L9  Choir           BACv1: Ranch Choir, 9-phase boot, .dass genome
L10 Braid           B₉ representation, Temperley-Lieb algebra, CoherenceQ

